MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 677

RESERVING FOR GOVERNMENT CENTER SITE PURPOSES OF THE MUNICIPALITY OF KAPATAGAN, LANAO DEL NORTE CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF KAPATAGAN, PROVINCE OF LANAO DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines do hereby withdraw from sale, entry, disposition, or settlement and reserve for government, center site purposes of the Municipality of Kapatagan, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in the Municipality of Kapatagan, Province of Lanao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, containing an aggregate area of Seventy One Thousand Three Hundred Eighty Six (71,386) square meters , more or less, subject to private rights, if any there be and to actual survey, which parcels of land are more particularly described as follows:

